            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div><p><em><a title="Games > Marathon [9 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/marathon">Marathon</a></em> for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [11,514 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [8,796 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [25,613 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a>, and <em><a title="Games > Pokemon Pokopia [5 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/pokemon-pokopia">Pokemon Pokopia</a></em> for <a title="Platforms > Switch 2 [1,049 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch-2">Switch 2</a> are the highlights of this week’s Japanese video game releases. <span id="more-1029875"></span></p><p>Also due out this week are <em><a title="Games > Never Grave: The Witch and The Curse [3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/never-grave-the-witch-and-the-curse">Never Grave: The Witch and The Curse</a></em> for PlayStation 5, Xbox Series, <a title="Platforms > PS4 [28,737 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PlayStation 4</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch [18,382 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a>, and PC,&nbsp;<em><a title="Games > Homura Hime [7 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/homura-hime">Homura Hime</a></em> for PC, and&nbsp;<em><a title="Games > Scott Pilgrim EX [3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/scott-pilgrim-ex">Scott Pilgrim EX</a></em> for PlayStation 5, Xbox Series, Switch 2, PlayStation 4, <a title="Platforms > Xbox One [14,418 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-one">Xbox One</a>, Switch, and PC.</p><p>Get the full list of this week’s Japanese game releases below. It should be noted that <a title="Companies > Gematsu" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/gematsu">Gematsu</a> will receive a small percentage of money from purchases made through Play-Asia links. You can also save five percent with our multi-use “<strong>GEMATSU2025</strong>” coupon code.</p><h2><span>Physical and Digital</span></h2><ul><li><i><a title="Games > Back to the Dawn [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/back-to-the-dawn">Back to the Dawn</a></i> (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/back-to-the-dawn-multi-language/13/70j547?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch 2</a>, <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/back-to-the-dawn-multi-language/13/70j545?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch</a>) – Game-key card on Switch 2. Launching digitally worldwide.<ul><li>Limited Edition (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/back-to-the-dawn-limited-edition-multi-language/13/70jcyp?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch 2</a>, <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/back-to-the-dawn-limited-edition-multi-language/13/70jcyl?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch</a>)</li><li>Asian Version<!-- AD: content -->
        <ul><li><ul><li>Standard Edition (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/back-to-the-dawn-multi-language/13/70j54d?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch 2</a>, <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/back-to-the-dawn-multi-language/13/70j54b?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch</a>)</li><li>Limited Edition (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/back-to-the-dawn-limited-edition-multi-language/13/70j8xz?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch 2</a>, <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/back-to-the-dawn-limited-edition-multi-language/13/70j8xx?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch</a>)</li></ul></li></ul></li></ul></li><li><em>Pokemon Pokopia</em> (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/pokemon-pokopia-multi-language/13/70j1g9?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch 2</a>) – Game-key card. Launching worldwide.<ul><li>North American Version (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/pokemon-pokopia/13/70j1ez?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch 2</a>)</li><li>European Version (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/pokemon-pokopia/13/70j1hx?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch 2</a>)</li></ul></li></ul><h2><span>Digital-Only</span></h2><ul><li><em><a title="Games > Citadelum" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/citadelum">Citadelum</a></em> (PS5, Xbox Series) – Launching worldwide.</li><li>Cut Corner Renovations USSR (PS4) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > Docked [3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/docked">Docked</a></em> (PS5, Xbox Series, PC [<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2487300/Docked/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>, <a href="https://store.epicgames.com/p/docked-047613" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Epic Games Store</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><i>Esoteric</i> Ebb (PC [<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2057760/Esoteric_Ebb/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em>Extra Coin</em> (PS5, Xbox Series, PS4, Xbox One, PC [<a href="https://www.xbox.com/en-us/games/store/extra-coin/9N2L3SLJ6XV3" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Microsoft Store</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em>Fly for Fly</em> (PS5, PS4) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em>Fortuna Magus</em> (PS5, Xbox Series, PS4, Xbox One, Switch, PC [<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3891350/Fortuna_Magus/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>, <a href="https://www.xbox.com/en-us/games/store/fortuna-magus/9NRCRH05QL97" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Microsoft Store</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > Gnaughty Gnomes [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/gnaughty-gnomes">Gnaughty Gnomes</a></em> (PC [<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3454480/Gnaughty_Gnomes/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em>Homura Hime</em> (PC [<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1820000/Homura_Hime/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em>IRON GUARD: Salvation</em> (<a title="Platforms > PS VR2 [275 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps-vr2">PS VR2</a>) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > The Legend of Khiimori [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/the-legend-of-khiimori">The Legend of Khiimori</a></em> Early Access (PC [<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2697000/The_Legend_of_Khiimori/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>, <a href="https://store.epicgames.com/p/windstorm-the-legend-of-khiimori-c6f4db" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Epic Games Store</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > Legacy of Kain: Defiance Remastered [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/legacy-of-kain-defiance-remastered">Legacy of Kain: Defiance Remastered</a></em> (PS5, Xbox Series, Switch, PC [<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3747730/Legacy_of_Kain_Defiance_Remastered/" target="_blank" r