The_Witch_and_The_Curse/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em>Our <a title="Genres > Adventure [2,912 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/adventure">Adventure</a>r Guild</em> (PS5) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em>Parcel Mania</em> (Switch) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > Planet of Lana II: Children of the Leaf [3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/planet-of-lana-ii-children-of-the-leaf">Planet of Lana II: Children of the Leaf</a></em> (PS5, Xbox Series, Switch 2, PS4, Xbox One, Switch, PC [<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2997230/Planet_of_Lana_II/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>, <a href="https://www.xbox.com/en-us/games/store/planet-of-lana-ii/9pl89b9hcz9w" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Microsoft Store</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em>Projected Dreams</em> (Switch) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > RAGER [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/rager">RAGER</a></em> (PS VR2) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > Ratcheteer DX [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/ratcheteer-dx">Ratcheteer DX</a></em> (Switch, PC [<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3166150/Ratcheteer_DX/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > Sea Fantasy [4 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/sea-fantasy">Sea Fantasy</a></em> (iOS, Android) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em>Scott Pilgrim EX</em> (PS5, Xbox Series, Switch 2, PS4, Switch, PC [<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2640950/Scott_Pilgrim_EX/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > Slay the Spire II [3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/slay-the-spire-ii">Slay the Spire II</a></em> Early Access (PC [<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2868840/Slay_the_Spire_2/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li><li>Sovereign Brain Empire (PS5) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > Sumerian Six [3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/sumerian-six">Sumerian Six</a></em> (PS5, Xbox Series) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > Timberborn [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/timberborn">Timberborn</a></em> (PC [<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1062090/Timberborn/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>, <a href="https://store.epicgames.com/p/timberborn" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Epic Games Store</a>, <a href="https://www.gog.com/en/game/timberborn" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GOG</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li></ul><p>The PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, and Switch titles listed above can be purchased through Japanese <a title="Platforms > PlayStation [49,687 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation">PlayStation</a> Network and <a title="Platforms > Nintendo [23,696 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo">Nintendo</a> accounts using prepaid cards:</p><ul><li>PlayStation Store cards (yen): <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/psn-card-1100-yen-playstation-network-japan/13/70dc0b?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">1,100</a> / <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/psn-card-3000-yen-playstation-network-japan/13/703xk5?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">3,000</a> / <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/%20-card-5000-yen-playstation-network-japan/13/703xk4?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">5,000</a> / <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/psn-card-10000-yen-playstation-network-japan/13/703xk3?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">10,000</a></li><li>Nintendo eShop cards (yen): <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/nintendo-eshop-card-1000-yen-japan-account/13/704a2v?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">1,000</a> / <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/nintendo-eshop-card-1500-yen-japan-account/13/70cte9?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">1,500</a> / <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/nintendo-eshop-card-3000-yen-japan-account/13/704a2w?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">3,000</a> / <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/nintendo-eshop-card-5000-yen-japan-account/13/705239?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">5,000</a> / <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/nintendo-eshop-card-9000-yen-japan-account/13/70bkw5?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">9,000</a></li></ul><h2><span>Demos, DLC, Updates, etc.</span></h2><ul><li><em><a title="Games > FATAL FRAME II: Crimson Butterfly REMAKE [3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/fatal-frame-ii-crimson-butterfly-remake">FATAL FRAME II: Crimson Butterfly REMAKE</a></em> Demo (PS5, Xbox Series, Switch 2, PC)</li><li><i><a title="Series > NINJA GAIDEN [16 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/series/ninja-gaiden">NINJA GAIDEN</a></i> 4 Downloadable Content “The Two <a title="Companies > Mas [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/mas">Mas</a>ters” (PS5, Xbox Series, PC)</li><li><em><a title="Games > Where Winds Meet [10 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/where-winds-meet">Where Winds Meet</a></em> “Hexi” Expansion (PS5, PC, iOS, Android)</li></ul></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2026/03/this-weeks-japanese-game-releases-marathon-pokemon-pokopia-more]]></content:encoded>
